"https", "video_ext": "mp4", "audio_ext": "none", "abr": 0, "vbr": 974.559, "resolution": "720x1280", "aspect_ratio": 0.56, "filesize_approx": 17051006, "http_headers": {"User-Agent": "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/143.0.0.0 Safari/537.36", "Accept": "text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,*/*;q=0.8", "Accept-Language": "en-us,en;q=0.5", "Sec-Fetch-Mode": "navigate", "Referer": "https://www.instagram.com/"}, "format": "dash-1588890805558083v - 720x1280 (DASH video)"}], "title": "Video by gigaqian", "description": "Quantum computing is basically about processing information simultaneously. That said, we’re playing with numerous unknowns and the main technology has been kept from the public. Origin Pilot is the first major step towards changing that in a meaningful way. It’s important to note that parts of this video oversimplify concepts to make them digestible. For instance, observing quantum entanglement typically breaks the entanglement - it’s more about the identification of the phenomenon that is so “spooky” and fascinating.\n#quantumcomputing #tech #learn #chinesetech #gigaqian", "duration": 139.969, "timestamp": 1772852281, "uploader_id": "70561211886", "uploader": "Giga Qian", "channel": "gigaqian", "like_count": 17227, "comment_count": 576, "comments": [{"author": "juniorlopez1960", "author_id": "2096824215", "id": "18083109725062634", "text": "Amen Amen Amen Thank You Jesus", "timestamp": 1775126703}, {"author": "johnwrites51", "author_id": "60543190907", "id": "18092509442156851", "text": "....so how many realities can we have at once???", "timestamp": 1774977529}, {"author": "jfjton", "author_id": "1222995549", "id": "17986304879971049", "text": "So how do we know an answer is correct once we observe it?", "timestamp": 1774959021}, {"author": "exploremore_northamerica", "author_id": "3677109442", "id": "18069285326290971", "text": "What’s interesting to me is that in 2015, it was projected that quantum computers would begin to dominate by 2030. Then the AI boom hit. Makes you wonder if that was on purpose to push out Chinese technology?", "timestamp": 1774935370}, {"author": "rayspeakz", "author_id": "973206924", "id": "18018059900661494", "text": "", "timestamp": 1774883289}, {"author": "miguel82red", "author_id": "36415734", "id": "18079617044527462", "text": "Bro the haircut 🔥fire fuego in Spanish looks amazing👏👏👏👏the voice bro you need to do some audible narration seriously such a mellifluous voice bra i dont just bust out the word for anyone 🔥giga and not in a gay way not that anything wrong with that last Seinfeld reference hes pretty foul after I found out about him dating shoshana not trying to bear judgement just my opinions side tracked yes triggered yes but  we all should be long live the people's republic of China. Ive always said i would have welcomed and much rather have been the united states of China Republic than the united of is ra hell.  I need to timeline jump again. Im back in hillvalley back to the future 2 alternate trump is biff. And we know Biffs way nicer 🔥", "timestamp": 1774876138}, {"author": "roman47681", "author_id": "69856242401", "id": "18107390500842130", "text": "China tortures, kills and eat dogs and cats.\n China should be NUKED .", "timestamp": 1774855218}, {"author": "jeannie_fromthebelt", "author_id": "80128906701", "id": "18092192789124490", "text": "I don’t have it. Where is mine?", "timestamp": 1774824119}], "thumbnails": [{"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/642560466_1856040658246850_158003465221638152_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi42NDB4MTEzNi5zZHIuZjcxODc4LmRlZmF1bHRfY292ZXJfZnJhbWUuYzIifQ&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=102&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gGaNMMxz35bJpG93SP1WycFMJ_ZEqxS-iYWk0IFb_Ahz_iiQjn6KzOcSMBSzngaA7c&_nc_ohc=LvelY1NnhDkQ7kNvwGMxSZD&_nc_gid=_eR68xh8UodG2pltLOm7sg&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af3Kf0w2O_f68xJsroNLin9